  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalistic, modern diablo-lite. Fight enemies, acquire upgrades, perfect your playstyle, explore levels and escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play your way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 100 different combinations of upgrades, all offering different strengths and weaknesses, you have the opportunity to play the way you want. Get in the thick of the fight, lurk on the outskirts and pick off your enemies from distance, or put yourself on the knife’s edge for greater power, it’s up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perfect your playstyle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal build with stats that augment what you want augmented and a freely iterative system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.poster.avif?t=1730405733\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.webm?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.mp4?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old-school made new</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built exclusively from letters in a modern reimagining of the ASCII style, combined with an amazing electronic soundtrack, experience classic retro vibes with modern quality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.poster.avif?t=1730405733\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.webm?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.mp4?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stress-free</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No wasted time: pause when you need to, respec when you want to, pick up the game easily and quickly and get a satisfying experience in chunks the length of a TV show.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalistic, modern diablo-lite. Fight enemies, acquire upgrades, perfect your playstyle, explore levels and escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play your way</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 100 different combinations of upgrades, all offering different strengths and weaknesses, you have the opportunity to play the way you want. Get in the thick of the fight, lurk on the outskirts and pick off your enemies from distance, or put yourself on the knife’s edge for greater power, it’s up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Perfect your playstyle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your ideal build with stats that augment what you want augmented and a freely iterative system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.poster.avif?t=1730405733\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.webm?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/d8f4850dbc73a3370eb41ee062770e18.mp4?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old-school made new</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built exclusively from letters in a modern reimagining of the ASCII style, combined with an amazing electronic soundtrack, experience classic retro vibes with modern quality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.poster.avif?t=1730405733\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.webm?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/949840/extras/cc479b0e42d6683de3be952c3197ed18.mp4?t=1730405733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stress-free</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No wasted time: pause when you need to, respec when you want to, pick up the game easily and quickly and get a satisfying experience in chunks the length of a TV show.</p>",
